# Performance Rules

React Compiler is enabled.

Rules:

- Trust React Compiler
- Avoid unnecessary useMemo
- Avoid unnecessary useCallback
- Avoid premature memoization
- Memoize only after profiling

Prefer:

- Suspense
- lazy()
- code splitting
- virtualization

Avoid:

```tsx
const value=useMemo(
 ()=>calculate(),
[]
)
```

unless profiling proves necessity